== English ==
=== Etymology ===
From the brand, [[w:Kleenex|Kleenex]], a popular brand of tissues.
=== Pronunciation ===
*[[IPA]]: /kli.nɛks/
=== Noun ===
'''kleenex'''
# (''US'') A generic term for a [[tissue]], irrespective of brand
#: ''Please could you hand me a '''kleenex''', my nose is running.''
